track.name: Trust in Me
comments: Perfection ! Etta was wonderful and her music still is...
This is for all the ladies out there ?
Perfection. Etta, you break me every time.
Excellent Etta. She could do just about anything musically.

Everybody who doesn't get goosebumps while listening to THIS voice is already dead an doesn't know it yet. 
Thank you, Etta!
'Twas a blue day for the blues when she left this world.But now she is making beautiful music in heaven :) You were/are  the best Etta!
A true torch singer, the best at it I may add~
Her voice is so clear and beautiful.  I hope you are well, Etta!
It's Friday December 23,2011. Just read Etta James is in very bad health. Many of us go way back with Etta.
